p.b: Increased glycolytic flux as an outcome of whole-genome duplication in yeast.
p.em: GC Conant and KH Wolfe, Mol Syst Biol 3:129,2007

body.p: This is the original model reproducing figure 2A of the article submitted by the authors. There exists a curated version with BIOMD0000000176 that reproduces figures 2A,3A and 3B from the publication. BIOMD0000000176 encompasses MODEL2426780967, MODEL2427021978, MODEL2427095802.

note.value: Model used by Conant and Wolfe, 2007, unpublished. Taken from Pritchard and Kell, 2002, Eur J Biochem 269: 3894-3904.
-Made all rate laws dependent on the product of WGD_E and Vmax
Results for the analysis in the above manuscript (Figure 2A) were obtained by manually changing the value of WGD_E to range between 0.65 and 1.0.
